# Tech Stack — SteadyStep

## Stack
- Vite + React 18 + TypeScript (strict)
- Tailwind CSS v3 (NOT v4)
- react-router-dom v6 (HashRouter)
- Recharts, lucide-react
- clsx + tailwind-merge as `cn()` in `src/lib/utils.ts`
- State: useState + useContext only
- Fonts: Source Serif 4 (serif), DM Sans (sans) via Google Fonts
- Deploy: Vercel static with vercel.json SPA rewrite

## Folder structure
src/
components/
ui/           # Button, Card, Input, Badge
layout/       # AppShell, TabBar, ScreenHeader
exercise/     # ExerciseCard, CircularTimer, RepCounter
chat/         # ChatBubble, QuickReplies
progress/    # BalanceScoreCard, WeeklyActivityChart, StreakBar, MilestoneList
screens/       # Onboarding, Home, Exercises, ExerciseSession, Chat, Progress, BalanceCheck, Profile
data/          # exercises, sessions, progress, messages, milestones (.ts)
context/       # UserContext.tsx
hooks/         # useTimer.ts
lib/           # utils.ts


## Conventions
- Absolute imports via `@/` alias
- Named default exports
- Pin Tailwind to ^3. If v4 syntax issues appear, downgrade.
